Module org.microbean.development.annotation
Package org.microbean.development.annotation

Annotation Interface Experimental

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,FIELD,LOCAL_VARIABLE,METHOD,PACKAGE,PARAMETER,TYPE,TYPE_PARAMETER,TYPE_USE}) public @interface Experimental
Indicates that the annotated element is experimental in some way.
